```sh
      cd /var/log
cd /etc
cd -  # Returns to /var/log
```

```sh
      # Assume /var/www is a symlink to /home/user/webcd -L /var/www      # Working directory shows as /var/www
pwd                 # Outputs: /var/www

cd -P /var/www      # Working directory resolves to actual path
pwd                 # Outputs: /home/user/web 

```
